22:26:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有無咩後遺症？</blockquote><br />\n第一日最難捱<br />\n第二第三日好啲<br />\n出返黎其實有少少好似啲人退休咁<br />\n冇咩motivation</blockquote><br />\n未打完<br />\n出返黎 其實個人仲好純咁</blockquote><br />\n醫生無話有咩事咩？"},{"pid":"c8e9de1bfcca64cd242d9e54246fb43d79b76695","tid":404154,"uid":55088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T22:31:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解幾日就放你出嚟？<br />\n你點證明自己再無自殺傾向？<br />\n我上次講話想自殺冇真係take action都入去困咗14日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n首先我入去係involuntary <br />\n要係入面72小時<br />\n每日會有Psychologist social worker nurese<br />\n睇下 觀察你既表現<br />\n再決定幾時會discharge 你<br />\n如果Psychologist覺得你有任何問題<br />\n佢地有權extend到14days <br />\n72小時後<br />\n你有權appeal 同judge講<br />\n由judge判斷你係咪要留14days or longer"},{"pid":"f194399ffb56a487159c3b0243fadf70491bd928","tid":404154,"uid":55088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T22:33:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解幾日就放你出嚟？<br />\n你點證明自己再無自殺傾向？<br />\n我上次講話想自殺冇真係take action都入去困咗14日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n首先我入去係involuntary <br />\n要係入面72小時<br />\n每日會有Psychologist social worker nurese<br />\n睇下 觀察你既表現<br />\n再決定幾時會discharge 你<br />\n如果Psychologist覺得你有任何問題<br />\n佢地有權extend到14days <br />\n72小時後<br />\n你有權appeal 同judge講<br />\n由judge判斷你係咪要留14days or longer</blockquote><br />\n我唔係香港<br />\n唔知你係邊"},{"pid":"37488bc2a9ba4704c435960d4e5d642074e4baf9","tid":404154,"uid":55088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T22:41:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因咩事想自殺<br />\n死過番生後有冇覺得睇開左</blockquote><br />\n咩事唔講啦<br />\n冇"},{"pid":"0922c5b1a5610ca4266084b6f71584231d07332e","tid":404154,"uid":63867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T22:42:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解幾日就放你出嚟？<br />\n你點證明自己再無自殺傾向？<br />\n我上次講話想自殺冇真係take action都入去困咗14日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n首先我入去係involuntary <br />\n要係入面72小時<br />\n每日會有Psychologist social worker nurese<br />\n睇下 觀察你既表現<br />\n再決定幾時會discharge 你<br />\n如果<span style=\"color: red;\">Psychologist</span>覺得你有任何問題<br />\n佢地有權extend到14days <br />\n72小時後<br />\n你有權appeal 同judge講<br />\n由judge判斷你係咪要留14days or longer</blockquote><br />\n應該係Psychiatrist<br />\n<br />\n同埋如果你係Section 31 入<br />\n應該係最多留7days<br />\n<br />\n之後如果assess左覺得有需要繼續觀察<br />\n可以extend一次 by section 32<br />\n 不多於21日<br />\n<br />\nor 比人cert. by section 36<br />\n咁就要留係醫院直至康復/情況穩定"},{"pid":"4d9abc8c6a25e4326604eb105ebab204bd32286f","tid":404154,"uid":55088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T22:45:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解幾日就放你出嚟？<br />\n你點證明自己再無自殺傾向？<br />\n我上次講話想自殺冇真係take action都入去困咗14日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n首先我入去係involuntary <br />\n要係入面72小時<br />\n每日會有Psychologist social worker nurese<br />\n睇下 觀察你既表現<br />\n再決定幾時會discharge 你<br />\n如果<span style=\"color: red;\">Psychologist</span>覺得你有任何問題<br />\n佢地有權extend到14days <br />\n72小時後<br />\n你有權appeal 同judge講<br />\n由judge判斷你係咪要留14days or longer</blockquote><br />\n應該係Psychiatrist<br />\n<br />\n同埋如果你係Section 31 入<br />\n應該係最多留7days<br />\n<br />\n之後如果assess左覺得有需要繼續觀察<br />\n可以extend一次 by section 32<br />\n 不多於21日<br />\n<br />\nor 比人cert. by section 36<br />\n咁就要留係醫院直至康復/情況穩定</blockquote><br />\n我係section 5150"},{"pid":"d81b021af848b62412af92cd3da3fc4efb246c1b","tid":404154,"uid":55088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T22:47:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有無咩後遺症？</blockquote><br />\n第一日最難捱<br />\n第二第三日好啲<br />\n出返黎其實有少少好似啲人退休咁<br />\n冇咩motivation</blockquote><br />\n未打完<br />\n出返黎 其實個人仲好純咁</blockquote><br />\n醫生無話有咩事咩？</blockquote><br />\nDepression anxiety"},{"pid":"ab32ccf19d72636c6de5671db5033d57f39ef2a4","tid":404154,"uid":2373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T23:16:02.000Z","msg":"入面有咩玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a0fe56d1652ae9d6b7986e0ec532079ecc945ef","tid":404154,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T23:56:02.000Z","msg":"係咪包食包住"},{"pid":"bc1adaad1cd7467ae6ac49f65a40f2be9ccab2fe","tid":404154,"uid":55088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T00:00:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>入面有咩玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇野玩<br />\n每日 會有輔導人員group activities <br />\n大約兩個鐘左右<br />\n其餘就係個度等時間過"},{"pid":"bc1702b3f56ac5d98d18eb55b41a3ef96935b1af","tid":404154,"uid":55088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T00:01:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪包食包住</blockquote><br />\n係,因為正常insurance 會包哂所有payment<br />\n理應1$你都唔洗比"},{"pid":"e2da2b2b96719957bf3c2a7afe2ef09e0bcb256f","tid":404154,"uid":112608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T00:07:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>入面有咩玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇野玩<br />\n每日 會有輔導人員group activities <br />\n大約兩個鐘左右<br />\n其餘就係個度等時間過</blockquote><br />\n咁多時間冇嘢做其實好容易另令人胡思亂想？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f790b0170d0cb28bfec0446db15e706b421b576b","tid":404154,"uid":112608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T00:08:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>入面有咩玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇野玩<br />\n每日 會有輔導人員group activities <br />\n大約兩個鐘左右<br />\n其餘就係個度等時間過</blockquote><br />\n咁多時間冇嘢做其實好容易另人胡思亂想？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c19e9133a3c4829b4169753d5be592aec3fe967","tid":404154,"uid":5858,"l